WEBVTT

00:02.120 --> 00:03.000
PREVIOUSLY ON "MARVEL'S
AGENTS OF S.H.I.E.L.D."...

00:03.000 --> 00:04.210
SO, GARRETT SAYS
YOUR FAMILY'S LIKE

00:04.210 --> 00:05.420
THE CABLE VERSION
OF THE KENNEDYS.

00:05.420 --> 00:06.620
Ward: MY OLDER BROTHER,
CHRISTIAN,

00:06.620 --> 00:08.080
HE DIDN'T BEAT UP
MY YOUNGER BROTHER.

00:08.080 --> 00:09.000
HE WAS CRUELER
THAN THAT.

00:09.000 --> 00:10.040
HE MADE ME DO IT.

00:10.040 --> 00:11.580
WELCOME HOME,
AGENT SIMMONS.

00:11.580 --> 00:12.420
HI, FITZ.

00:12.420 --> 00:13.040
IS THAT
REALLY YOU?

00:13.040 --> 00:14.620
WHO ELSE WOULD IT BE?

00:14.620 --> 00:16.920
ANYONE MIND TELLING ME WHAT THE
BLOODY HELL SHE'S DOING HERE?

00:16.920 --> 00:18.330
BOBBI'S ONE
OF OUR BEST AGENTS.

00:18.330 --> 00:20.580
HUNTER EVER TELL YOU STORIES
ABOUT HIS SHE-DEVIL EX-WIFE?

00:20.580 --> 00:21.960
ALL THE TIME.

00:21.960 --> 00:23.080
DAMN.

00:23.080 --> 00:24.380
I'VE GOT A SENATOR

00:24.380 --> 00:26.540
WITH VERY DEEP POCKETS
THAT WANTS COULSON.

00:26.540 --> 00:27.750
YOUR FATHER IS ALIVE.

00:27.750 --> 00:29.120
AND SOMEDAY,
IF YOU LET ME,

00:29.120 --> 00:30.500
I'LL TAKE YOU TO HIM.

00:38.620 --> 00:42.830
Talbot: I WAS HERE IN 2012
WHEN THE SKY TORE OPEN

00:42.830 --> 00:44.380
AND THE CHITAURI
RAINED DOWN ON US.

00:44.380 --> 00:46.960
ALIENS.

00:46.960 --> 00:49.170
ALIENS WERE RUNNING
THROUGH THE STREETS,

00:49.170 --> 00:52.040
AND IT WAS THEN THAT
S.H.I.E.L.D. REVEALED THEMSELVES

00:52.040 --> 00:53.580
AND STOOD WITH THE AVENGERS,

00:53.580 --> 00:57.080
LEADING US TO BELIEVE THAT
WE COULD PUT OUR FAITH IN THEM,

00:57.080 --> 00:58.830
WHICH WE DID.

00:58.830 --> 01:00.710
WE STOOD IDLY BY

01:00.710 --> 01:03.880
WHILE THEY COLLECTED
SUPER-POWERED INDIVIDUALS,

01:03.880 --> 01:05.459
GARNERED ALIEN WEAPONS,

01:05.459 --> 01:09.040
BUILT BASES ON VIRTUALLY
EVERY CONTINENT.

01:09.040 --> 01:12.620
WE THOUGHT S.H.I.E.L.D.
WAS PROTECTING US, BUT IN TRUTH,

01:12.620 --> 01:15.920
THEY TOOK ADVANTAGE
OF OUR GOOD FAITH,

01:15.920 --> 01:18.960
AND THEY STILL ARE.

01:18.960 --> 01:21.830
ITALY TAKES NOTE
OF YOUR REPORT, GENERAL.

01:21.830 --> 01:25.000
NOW, YOU SAY
THAT YOU'VE SEEN S.H.I.E.L.D.,

01:25.000 --> 01:27.250
EVEN FOUGHT AGAINST THEM.

01:27.250 --> 01:29.040
BUT WHERE IS THE PROOF?

01:29.040 --> 01:32.080
[ WHIRRING ]
WHERE IS -- AAH!
CHE DIAVOLO!

01:33.170 --> 01:36.120
HELP!

01:36.120 --> 01:37.670
[ Echoing ] HELP ME!

01:37.670 --> 01:39.210
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]
Woman:
S.H.I.E.L.D.'s HERE!

01:39.210 --> 01:40.460
FREEZE!

01:40.460 --> 01:41.960
[ WHIRRING ]

01:41.960 --> 01:43.080
[ GROANS ]

01:44.960 --> 01:47.170
[ WHIRRING, MAN SCREAMS ]

01:48.170 --> 01:49.960
[ WHIRRING, WOMAN SCREAMS ]

01:49.960 --> 01:51.580
GO TO THE EXIT IN THE CORNER.

01:51.580 --> 01:53.000
GO!

01:53.000 --> 01:54.290
[ WHIRRING ]

01:55.330 --> 01:56.710
[ WHIRRING, WOMAN SCREAMS ]

01:56.710 --> 01:57.920
COME HERE.

02:00.580 --> 02:03.750
S.H.I.E.L.D. IS DONE HIDING.

02:05.380 --> 02:07.380
[ WHIRRING ]

02:29.040 --> 02:32.830
5:30 ON THE DOT
EVERY MORNING.

02:32.830 --> 02:35.580
BUT THERE'S NO CLOCK,
NO LIGHT,

02:35.580 --> 02:37.420
NO WAY HE CAN KNOW
WHAT TIME IT IS.

02:37.420 --> 02:38.920
YOU'VE BEEN WATCHING HIM?

02:38.920 --> 02:41.620
EVERY DAY BEFORE I LEFT,
EVERY DAY SINCE I GOT BACK.

02:41.620 --> 02:43.000
I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU DO IT,

02:43.000 --> 02:44.960
GOING DOWN THERE,
TALKING TO HIM.

02:44.960 --> 02:48.670
SACRIFICES WE MAKE
FOR VALUABLE INTEL, RIGHT?

02:48.670 --> 02:54.040
JEMMA SIMMONS
UNDERCOVER AT HYDRA.

02:54.040 --> 02:55.960
I THOUGHT I WAS A DEAD WOMAN
AT LEAST FOUR TIMES.

02:55.960 --> 02:58.120
I'M GLAD YOU'RE NOT.

02:58.120 --> 02:59.880
ME TOO.

02:59.880 --> 03:02.790
BE CAREFUL
WITH HIM, SKYE.

03:02.790 --> 03:04.540
I AM.

03:04.540 --> 03:06.960
[ ALARM BLARING ]

03:06.960 --> 03:08.040
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

03:08.040 --> 03:09.830
THERE'S BEEN AN ATTACK
ON THE U.N.

03:12.710 --> 03:13.920
AN ATTACK TODAY OF THE U.N.

03:13.920 --> 03:16.790
LEFT SIX DEAD
AND DOZENS INJURED.

03:16.790 --> 03:19.250
MANY HAVE NOT BEEN IDENTIFIED,

03:19.250 --> 03:20.620
S.H.I.E.L.D.'S
BIGGEST OPPONENT,

03:20.620 --> 03:24.380
U.S. AIR FORCE
BRIGADIER GENERAL GLENN TALBOT.

03:24.380 --> 03:25.960
SIR, THIS WASN'T US,
WAS IT?

03:25.960 --> 03:28.540
NO, THIS IS HYDRA
LOOKING FOR REVENGE.

03:28.540 --> 03:31.000
BEST GUESS --
DANIEL WHITEHALL HAD HIS PEOPLE

03:31.000 --> 03:31.960
IMPERSONATE S.H.I.E.L.D.

03:31.960 --> 03:33.710
TO PUT THE WORLD'S ATTENTION
BACK ON US.

03:33.710 --> 03:35.210
SO MUCH FOR STAYING
IN THE SHADOWS.

03:35.210 --> 03:37.750
SOMEBODY BRING THIS
FROM HOME?

03:39.790 --> 03:42.170
I WANT YOU TWO
SCOURING GOVERNMENT CHANNELS,

03:42.170 --> 03:43.210
SEE WHAT WE'RE
UP AGAINST.

03:43.210 --> 03:44.540
ON IT, SIR.

03:44.540 --> 03:46.420
AND, SKYE, THIS MEANS
THE ALIEN WRITING --

03:46.420 --> 03:47.460
BACK BURNER.

03:47.460 --> 03:48.960
JUST UNTIL WE GET THIS
UNDER CONTROL.

03:50.380 --> 03:51.620
JUST SAW THE NEWS.

03:51.620 --> 03:52.830
WE'RE NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR THIS,
ARE WE, SIR?

03:52.830 --> 03:54.920
DIDN'T THINK SO.
JUST WANTED TO TRIPLE-CHECK.

03:54.920 --> 03:56.830
MARCUS SCARLOTTI
WAS BEHIND THE ATTACK.

03:56.830 --> 03:57.880
AN ASSASSIN --

03:57.880 --> 03:59.920
ALMOST KILLED BARTON
A FEW YEARS BACK.

03:59.920 --> 04:02.830
RUNS A TEAM OF MERCENARIES --
MOSTLY FOR HYDRA.

04:02.830 --> 04:04.920
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

04:04.920 --> 04:06.750
AH.

04:06.750 --> 04:08.290
THE BODIES
JUST DISINTEGRATE.

04:08.290 --> 04:11.250
I SAW REFERENCES TO THIS WEAPON
IN HYDRA'S LAB.

04:11.250 --> 04:13.670
YEAH, SENT FROM
THEIR DEMOLITIONS EXPERT,

04:13.670 --> 04:14.790
UH, TOSHIRO...

04:14.790 --> 04:15.880
TOSHIRO MORI.

04:15.880 --> 04:17.880
I'VE CROSSED PATHS
WITH HIM BEFORE.

04:17.880 --> 04:19.420
HE HAS A LAB IN OKINAWA.

04:19.420 --> 04:21.829
GOOD. THEN THAT'S
WHERE YOU'RE GOING.

04:21.829 --> 04:23.500
WE NEED TO FIND THE LOCATION
OF THE NEXT ATTACK

04:23.500 --> 04:25.250
AND STOP IT
BEFORE IT HAPPENS.

04:25.250 --> 04:26.620
MAY'S TAKING POINT
ON THIS OP.

04:26.620 --> 04:28.250
YOU CAN MEET HER AND HUNTER
IN THE HANGAR.

04:28.250 --> 04:29.920
HUNTER'S GOING?

04:31.540 --> 04:33.710
GOT IT.
THANK YOU, SIR.

04:35.960 --> 04:37.290
I NEED YOU
TO DIG THROUGH

04:37.290 --> 04:39.580
THE HARD DRIVE YOU BROUGHT BACK
FROM WHITEHALL'S LAB.

04:39.580 --> 04:41.960
I'LL FIND OUT WHATEVER I CAN
ABOUT THOSE WEAPONS.

04:43.880 --> 04:44.880
[ TABLET BEEPS ]

04:44.880 --> 04:46.620
COULSON, QUICK QUESTION.

04:46.620 --> 04:48.380
NO, THIS WASN'T US.

04:48.380 --> 04:50.080
OH, THA--
UH, GREAT.

04:50.080 --> 04:53.170
UM...MAY SAID I'D BE GOING
ON A MISSION WITH BOBBI?

04:53.170 --> 04:54.920
IS THAT GONNA BE
A PROBLEM?

04:54.920 --> 04:56.620
DID SHE SAY
IT WAS GONNA BE A PROBLEM?

04:56.620 --> 04:58.580
I WON'T DIGNIFY THAT
WITH A RESPONSE.

04:58.580 --> 05:00.040
SO...SHE...DIDN'T?

05:00.040 --> 05:03.460
I THINK WE ALL KNOW
HOW YOU FEEL ABOUT YOUR EX-WIFE,

05:03.460 --> 05:06.250
BUT IF IT'S TOO COMPLICATED,
THEN BY ALL MEANS.

05:07.710 --> 05:09.000
WHITEHALL'S
ON THE ATTACK.

05:10.170 --> 05:12.620
AND INSTEAD OF USING HIS OWN
FORCES TO DESTROY S.H.I.E.L.D.,

05:12.620 --> 05:15.080
HE'S HAVING THE REST
OF THE WORLD DO IT FOR HIM.

05:21.960 --> 05:24.330
YOU'RE LUCKY
TO BE ALIVE, GENERAL.

05:24.330 --> 05:25.880
MY LUCKY DAY.

05:25.880 --> 05:27.040
IT WAS MY UNDERSTANDING

05:27.040 --> 05:29.460
THAT YOU HAD S.H.I.E.L.D.
UNDER CONTROL.

05:29.460 --> 05:30.880
OTHERWISE,
I DON'T KNOW WHY

05:30.880 --> 05:32.460
I PERSUADED
THE ARMED SERVICES COMMITTEE

05:32.460 --> 05:34.830
TO GIVE YOUR UNIT
SUCH EXTRAORDINARY FUNDING.

05:34.830 --> 05:37.290
BECAUSE IT WORKED
UNTIL THIS MORNING.

05:37.290 --> 05:39.750
I DON'T THINK ANYTHING BEFORE
TODAY MATTERS NOW, DOES IT?

05:39.750 --> 05:41.830
S.H.I.E.L.D. ATTACKED
THE UNITED NATIONS,

05:41.830 --> 05:43.500
FOR GOD'S SAKE,
UNDER YOUR WATCH.

05:43.500 --> 05:46.540
PEOPLE WHO ATTACKED US
MAY NOT HAVE BEEN S.H.I.E.L.D.

05:46.540 --> 05:47.920
IT'S TIME I STEP IN.

05:47.920 --> 05:50.290
AND DO WHAT?
CONTROL THE SITUATION.

05:50.290 --> 05:52.500
NOW THAT S.H.I.E.L.D.'s
BACK IN THE SPOTLIGHT,

05:52.500 --> 05:54.080
THE PRESS IS GONNA TAKE THIS
AND RUN WITH IT.

05:54.080 --> 05:55.000
YOU'RE WORRIED
THEY'RE GONNA FIND OUT

05:55.000 --> 05:56.210
ABOUT YOUR BROTHER,
AREN'T YOU?

05:56.210 --> 06:00.460
WHAT WORRIES ME
IS THAT YOU EVEN KNOW ABOUT HIM.

06:00.460 --> 06:03.790
I DON'T PLAY POLITICS,
SENATOR.

06:03.790 --> 06:07.620
I HAVEN'T SAID ONE WORD
ABOUT YOUR BROTHER TO ANYONE,

06:07.620 --> 06:08.750
AND I DON'T INTEND TO.

06:08.750 --> 06:11.580
THE TRUTH IS, GENERAL,
YOU CAN'T ASSURE ME OF ANYTHING.

06:11.580 --> 06:14.330
IT'S TIME I DO WHAT
I SHOULD'VE DONE MONTHS AGO --

06:14.330 --> 06:17.080
PUT S.H.I.E.L.D.
IN THE GROUND FOR GOOD.

06:25.000 --> 06:26.790
S.H.I.E.L.D. IS
A TERRORIST ORGANIZATION,

06:26.790 --> 06:28.210
AND THEY SHOULD BE TREATED
AS SUCH.

06:28.210 --> 06:29.750
Man: IS THAT WHAT YOU PLAN
TO SPEAK ABOUT

06:29.750 --> 06:31.750
AT THE U.N.'s
EMERGENCY SESSION TOMORROW?

06:31.750 --> 06:34.330
WHAT I PLAN TO DO
IS LAY OUT A PROPOSAL

06:34.330 --> 06:36.710
FOR A MULTI-NATIONAL
POLICE FORCE

06:36.710 --> 06:38.710
THAT WILL TARGET
THOSE SUSPECTED

06:38.710 --> 06:40.420
OF TIES WITH S.H.I.E.L.D.

06:40.420 --> 06:42.620
USING ANY
AND ALL MEANS NECESSARY.

06:42.620 --> 06:44.460
Beckers:
ANYONE SUSPECTED OF TIES?

06:44.460 --> 06:45.620
AND WHO DETERMINES THAT?

06:45.620 --> 06:47.540
BELGIUM WILL NEVER ACCEPT
THIS PROPOSAL.

06:47.540 --> 06:50.540
IT DESTROYS THE VERY IDEA
OF CITIZENS' RIGHTS.

06:50.540 --> 06:52.670
Senator Ward:
MR. BECKERS, IF YOU WANT
TO WELCOME S.H.I.E.L.D.

06:52.670 --> 06:55.540
AT YOUR BORDERS WITH OPEN ARMS,
BE MY GUEST,

06:55.540 --> 06:58.330
BUT THIS INFESTATION
NEEDS TO BE EXTERMINATED.

06:58.330 --> 07:01.250
GUESS BEING A DOUCHE-BAG
RUNS IN THE FAMILY.

07:01.250 --> 07:02.580
ARE YOU SURPRISED?

07:02.580 --> 07:04.710
WARD'S BROTHER NEVER CARED
ABOUT S.H.I.E.L.D. BEFORE.

07:04.710 --> 07:05.670
NOT OPENLY.

07:05.670 --> 07:08.170
YEAH, BUT HUNTER SAID
THAT TALBOT WAS WORKING WITH

07:08.170 --> 07:09.580
A SENATOR
WHO HAD DEEP POCKETS.

07:09.580 --> 07:10.620
YOU THINK IT'S HIM?

07:10.620 --> 07:12.380
I DO.

07:12.380 --> 07:13.750
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

07:13.750 --> 07:15.920
MONTHS REBUILDING,
AND THIS IS S.H.I.E.L.D.

07:15.920 --> 07:19.380
FEW OPERATIVES HERE,
NOT MANY MORE OUT THERE.

07:19.380 --> 07:21.040
IF SENATOR WARD'S
PROPOSAL PASSES...

07:21.040 --> 07:22.380
IT'LL BE A WITCH-HUNT.

07:22.380 --> 07:24.120
EVERY MILITARY ORGANIZATION
ON THE PLANET

07:24.120 --> 07:27.040
WILL HAVE A LICENSE TO KICK
OUR OPERATIVES' DOORS DOWN

07:27.040 --> 07:29.210
AND SHOOT THEM
ON THE SPOT.

07:29.210 --> 07:30.830
I CAN'T LET THAT HAPPEN.

07:32.540 --> 07:36.120
I'LL TALK TO WARD, SEE IF HE HAS
ANY INTEL ON HIS BROTHER.

07:36.120 --> 07:38.960
AND, SKYE...

07:38.960 --> 07:41.290
KEEP THE FOCUS
ON HIS FAMILY, NOT YOURS.

07:46.500 --> 07:48.040
[ TABLET BEEPS ]

07:50.290 --> 07:51.830
AGENT WALTERS.
Director.

07:51.830 --> 07:53.330
HOW'S THE NETHERLANDS?

07:53.330 --> 07:55.120
Same as always, sir.
Lots of bikes, lots of weed.

07:55.120 --> 07:56.920
I assume this is about
the anti-S.H.I.E.L.D. proposal.

07:56.920 --> 07:58.830
WE CAN'T TAKE ANY CHANCES.
[ SIGHS ]

07:58.830 --> 08:01.670
SEND OUT THE WORD TO YOUR TEAM.
GO DARK. SEEK REFUGE.

08:01.670 --> 08:04.000
REESTABLISH CONTACT
IN 24 HOURS.

08:04.000 --> 08:05.420
Copy that, sir.

08:05.420 --> 08:07.670
AND, AGENT WALTERS,
STAY SAFE.

08:12.620 --> 08:14.620
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

08:19.000 --> 08:20.620
YOU LOOK GOOD.

08:22.540 --> 08:24.420
OH, YEAH?

08:24.420 --> 08:25.500
CHEERS.

08:27.500 --> 08:30.290
AND, YOU KNOW, WITH THE...
BLOND AND EVERYTHING,

08:30.290 --> 08:33.580
YOU DON'T LOOK
TOO BAD YOURSELF.

08:33.580 --> 08:36.620
IT'S NICE OF YOU TO SAY.

08:36.620 --> 08:39.210
BECAUSE I HEARD YOU'VE BEEN
TELLING PEOPLE I'M A HELL BEAST.

08:41.289 --> 08:44.460
UH...NO, I D--
I DON'T THINK SO.

08:44.460 --> 08:47.620
I DEFINITELY DIDN'T USE
THOSE WORDS SPECIFICALLY.

08:47.620 --> 08:50.540
THAT DOESN'T EVEN SOUND LIKE
SOMETHING I'D SAY, REALLY.

08:52.460 --> 08:55.290
SO, YOU VOUCHED FOR ME,

08:55.290 --> 08:56.670
KNEW I WAS WITH S.H.I.E.L.D.
THE WHOLE TIME?

08:56.670 --> 08:58.920
I'M HONESTLY SURPRISED
YOU STAYED THIS LONG.

08:58.920 --> 09:00.620
WELL, YOU KNOW,
I'M HERE FOR NOW,

09:00.620 --> 09:02.750
BUT KEEPING MY OPTIONS
OPEN, OBVIOUSLY.

09:02.750 --> 09:04.620
YOU ALWAYS DO.

09:04.620 --> 09:05.750
[ SCOFFS ]

09:05.750 --> 09:07.330
IF WE'RE
GONNA DO THIS NOW,

09:07.330 --> 09:09.040
AT LEAST LET ME
GRAB A BEER FIRST.

09:09.040 --> 09:11.880
I'M GONNA GO CHECK ON MAY.

09:16.540 --> 09:17.830
WE'LL BE
TOUCHING DOWN SOON.

09:17.830 --> 09:19.040
OKAY.

09:21.710 --> 09:23.170
[ SIGHS ]

09:25.330 --> 09:26.500
YOU EVER BEEN MARRIED?

09:29.620 --> 09:31.000
STILL TALK TO HIM?

09:32.880 --> 09:35.790
RIGHT.

09:35.790 --> 09:37.540
GOOD ADVICE.

09:37.540 --> 09:39.540
[ WHISPERING INDISTINCTLY ]

09:48.210 --> 09:49.540
MORNING, FITZ.

09:51.540 --> 09:52.620
HEY.

09:55.540 --> 09:57.000
[ DEVICE BEEPS ]

09:57.000 --> 10:01.500
IS THAT THE, UH...
HARD DRIVE THAT YOU STOLE?

10:01.500 --> 10:02.710
COULSON ASKED ME
TO SEARCH IT

10:02.710 --> 10:04.500
FOR ANYTHING RELATED
TO THE ATTACKS.

10:04.500 --> 10:07.040
UM, I WAS HOPING
YOU COULD HELP.

10:07.040 --> 10:09.170
THAT IS, IF YOU'RE NOT TOO --
I MEAN --

10:09.170 --> 10:11.500
YEAH, UM,
IF YOU NEED M-MY HELP,

10:11.500 --> 10:13.040
I SUPPOSE
I'VE GOT SOME TIME.

10:13.040 --> 10:15.080
WELL, UNFORTUNATELY,

10:15.080 --> 10:17.880
THE DRIVE WAS DAMAGED
DURING OUR ESCAPE.

10:17.880 --> 10:21.670
WE'LL HAVE TO REPAIR IT
TO ACCESS ANY OF ITS I-INTEL.

10:21.670 --> 10:23.580
WHAT?

10:23.580 --> 10:25.330
JUST, UM...

10:25.330 --> 10:28.420
YOU LOOK DIFFERENT.
THAT'S ALL.

10:28.420 --> 10:30.620
OH.

10:30.620 --> 10:32.170
NOT "BAD" DIFFERENT.
JUST...

10:34.670 --> 10:36.540
OKAY.

10:38.620 --> 10:43.330
UH...WE PROBABLY NEED TO FIRST
LOOK AT THE, UH --

10:43.330 --> 10:44.710
THE SHOCK SENSOR.

10:44.710 --> 10:46.710
UM, NO, THE, UM --
VOICE ACTUATOR?

10:46.710 --> 10:48.460
NO, UM, JEMMA, CAN YOU --

10:48.460 --> 10:49.420
I'M -- I'M SORRY.

10:49.420 --> 10:51.330
I KNOW. IT'S JUST
YOU SAID YOU NEEDED MY HELP.

10:51.330 --> 10:52.710
NO, I DO.
YEAH, OF COURSE I DO.

10:52.710 --> 10:59.710
IT'S THE...MICRO, UH...
THIS THING HERE.

10:59.710 --> 11:01.920
OH, YEAH. I SEE.

11:01.920 --> 11:04.000
I...SEE THAT.

11:04.000 --> 11:05.330
Skye: WE NEED TO TALK ABOUT
YOUR BROTHER.

11:05.330 --> 11:07.420
WHICH ONE?

11:07.420 --> 11:09.420
YOUR OLDER BROTHER --
THE SENATOR.

11:09.420 --> 11:12.880
CHRISTIAN.

11:12.880 --> 11:14.500
WHY?

11:14.500 --> 11:16.000
WHAT HAPPENED?

11:16.000 --> 11:17.460
JUST NEED
BASIC INFORMATION --

11:17.460 --> 11:19.540
HABITS, PLACES
HE FREQUENTLY VISITS --

11:19.540 --> 11:20.460
STUFF LIKE THAT.

11:20.460 --> 11:23.540
YOU NEED TO STAY AWAY
FROM HIM.

11:23.540 --> 11:25.420
HE'S NOT WHAT HE SEEMS.

11:25.420 --> 11:26.710
HE ALWAYS HAS AN ANGLE,

11:26.710 --> 11:29.500
AND IF HE THINKS
THAT YOU CAN LEAD HIM TO ME --

11:29.500 --> 11:32.380
THIS ISN'T ABOUT YOU.
ISN'T IT?

11:32.380 --> 11:34.500
DON'T YOU REMEMBER
WHAT HAPPENED AT THE WELL,

11:34.500 --> 11:35.710
WHAT HE MADE ME DO?

11:35.710 --> 11:39.080
HE GETS JOY FROM ONE THING --
HURTING PEOPLE.

11:40.920 --> 11:44.420
SO, TELL ME, PLEASE.

11:44.420 --> 11:46.460
DOES HE KNOW I'M HERE?

11:46.460 --> 11:47.920
NOT HOW IT WORKS, WARD.

11:47.920 --> 11:50.080
YOU ANSWER MY QUESTIONS,
REMEMBER?

11:50.080 --> 11:52.250
AND I ALWAYS DO.
I ALWAYS TELL YOU THE TRUTH,

11:52.250 --> 11:53.750
BUT IF CHRISTIAN KNOWS
THAT I'M HERE --

11:53.750 --> 11:55.380
YOU ALWAYS
TELL ME THE TRUTH?

11:55.380 --> 11:56.710
YES.
[ SCOFFS ]

11:56.710 --> 12:00.120
I PROMISED YOU I'D NEVER LIE
TO YOU, AND I HAVEN'T.

12:06.380 --> 12:09.580
WHAT'S THIS...REALLY ABOUT?

12:09.580 --> 12:12.500
I NEED INFORMATION
ABOUT YOUR BROTHER --

12:12.500 --> 12:15.000
PEOPLE, CONNECTIONS.

12:15.000 --> 12:16.210
IS THIS
ABOUT YOUR FATHER?

12:17.500 --> 12:20.080
'CAUSE I WASN'T LYING
ABOUT HIM.

12:20.080 --> 12:22.330
HE'S ALIVE, AND HE'S --

12:22.330 --> 12:23.790
HE'S A MURDERER.

12:25.500 --> 12:28.330
YOU FORGOT TO MENTION
THAT DETAIL.

12:28.330 --> 12:30.710
[ EXHALES SOFTLY ]

12:30.710 --> 12:32.420
YOU FOUND HIM.

12:35.330 --> 12:37.420
HE DIDN'T GIVE US WHAT WE NEEDED
ON HIS BROTHER.

12:37.420 --> 12:40.000
TRUST ME.
HE GAVE US MORE THAN YOU THINK.

12:40.000 --> 12:42.670
AND YOU'RE SLIPPING
OFF TRACK, SKYE.

12:42.670 --> 12:44.420
STAY ON-MISSION.

12:46.000 --> 12:49.000
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

12:49.000 --> 12:52.830
TOSHIRO HAS THE WEAPONS
FROM THE U.N. ATTACK,

12:52.830 --> 12:54.170
SO WE HAVE TWO OPTIONS --

12:54.170 --> 12:55.500
ONE -- FIREFIGHT.

12:55.500 --> 12:57.710
SURPRISE THEM,
TAKE DOWN AS MANY AS WE CAN

12:57.710 --> 12:59.750
BEFORE THEY BRING OUT
HEAVY ARTILLERY.

12:59.750 --> 13:02.380
AND OPTION TWO?
JUST TO HEAR IT.

13:02.380 --> 13:04.790
I USE MY HYDRA COVER --
A COVER THAT COULD BE BLOWN.

13:04.790 --> 13:05.920
THAT'S WHY I LIKE
OPTION ONE.

13:05.920 --> 13:08.210
ON THE OTHER HAND,
I KNOW TOSHIRO.

13:08.210 --> 13:11.620
THE BEST WAY TO GET HIM TO LEAK
INTEL IS TO GET HIM BRAGGING.

13:11.620 --> 13:13.000
I THINK
IT'S WORTH THE RISK.

13:13.000 --> 13:15.330
SHE CAN HANDLE IT.
DECEPTION'S HER FORTE.

13:17.040 --> 13:19.540
UH, I-I MEAN THAT SINCERELY,
NOT PASSIVE-AGGRESSIVELY.

13:19.540 --> 13:21.710
AS IN, IT'S A GOOD ATTRIBUTE
FOR A SPY TO --

13:21.710 --> 13:24.000
[ SIGHS ]
BLOODY HELL.

13:24.000 --> 13:28.040
YOU CAN GO IN,
BUT IF ANYTHING'S OFF,

13:28.040 --> 13:29.330
WE'RE COMING AFTER YOU.

13:30.210 --> 13:32.380
THEY'LL SEARCH YOU
FOR WEAPONS.

13:35.170 --> 13:37.080
[ MORSE SIGHS ]

13:37.080 --> 13:38.620
DON'T DIE OUT THERE,
ALL RIGHT?

13:44.330 --> 13:46.330
[ INSECTS CHIRPING ]

13:54.330 --> 13:56.500
DATA INTERCEPT'S UP
AND RUNNING.

13:56.500 --> 13:58.670
WE HAVE AUDIO AND VISUAL
FROM THE SECURITY CAMERAS

13:58.670 --> 14:03.000
AND ACCESS TO ANY INCOMING
CELLULAR COMMUNICATIONS.

14:09.170 --> 14:12.250
TOSHIRO-SAN.

14:14.420 --> 14:16.420
[ SPEAKING JAPANESE ]

14:16.420 --> 14:18.210
SHE SPEAKS JAPANESE?

14:18.210 --> 14:20.210
SHE HAS
THIS ANNOYING KNACK

14:20.210 --> 14:22.540
FOR PICKING THINGS UP
VERY QUICKLY.

14:22.540 --> 14:24.880
[ SPEAKING JAPANESE ]

14:33.830 --> 14:34.830
NO.

14:34.830 --> 14:36.420
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

14:40.500 --> 14:42.040
STILL LIKE OPTION TWO?

14:49.170 --> 14:52.120
DO YOU STILL HAVE
THAT PAN-FIRED GREEN TEA?

14:52.120 --> 14:54.790
IT'S FROM THE
SHIZUOKA PREFECTURE, RIGHT?

14:54.790 --> 14:57.120
YOU ALWAYS REMEMBER
EVERY LITTLE DETAIL.

14:57.880 --> 14:59.170
TRY BEING MARRIED
TO SOMEBODY

14:59.170 --> 15:00.830
WHO REMEMBERS
EVERY LITTLE DETAIL.

15:00.830 --> 15:01.830
IT'S NOT THAT CHARMING.

15:01.830 --> 15:03.040
[ SIGHS ]

15:03.040 --> 15:04.790
YOU THINK I'M BEING PETTY,
DON'T YOU?

15:04.790 --> 15:05.960
WELL, I'M NOT.

15:05.960 --> 15:08.210
I DON'T HAVE A PROBLEM
WITH BOB KISSING THAT GUY.

15:08.210 --> 15:10.380
GOOD. BECAUSE YOU HAD A HICKEY
ON YOUR NECK FOR A WEEK

15:10.380 --> 15:12.250
AFTER OUR MISSION
IN MIAMI.

15:12.250 --> 15:14.170
EXCUSE ME
FOR DOING MY JOB THOROUGHLY...

15:14.170 --> 15:15.750
AND WITH STYLE.

15:24.000 --> 15:28.670
THE TEA NEEDS TO STEEP
FOR AT LEAST SEVEN MINUTES.

15:28.670 --> 15:30.380
MM.

15:30.380 --> 15:32.080
PERFECT TIME FOR US
TO TALK BUSINESS, THEN.

15:32.080 --> 15:34.580
FORGIVE ME, BUT I'D LIKE
TO CLEAR SOMETHING UP FIRST.

15:34.580 --> 15:37.830
YOU SEE, THERE'S
A NASTY RUMOR GOING AROUND

15:37.830 --> 15:39.540
THAT YOU ARE ACTUALLY WORKING
FOR S.H.I.E.L.D.

15:39.540 --> 15:41.880
TOSHI, PLEASE.

15:41.880 --> 15:43.830
AREN'T WE ALL WORKING
FOR S.H.I.E.L.D.?

15:43.830 --> 15:45.750
DIDN'T YOU SEE THE PAPERS
THIS MORNING?

15:45.750 --> 15:47.290
SCARLOTTI AND HIS TEAM
WERE ON THE FRONT PAGE

15:47.290 --> 15:48.830
WITH THAT SILLY EAGLE
ON THEIR CHESTS.

15:50.080 --> 15:53.170
BUT THOSE WEAPONS
THEY HAD...

15:53.170 --> 15:55.080
YOUR WORK, I PRESUME?

15:56.670 --> 15:58.120
HOW COULD YOU TELL?

15:58.120 --> 16:00.670
Hunter: THIS POOR SAP'S BUYING
EVERY WORD SHE SAYS.

16:00.670 --> 16:01.920
THAT'S WHAT WE WANT.

16:01.920 --> 16:04.040
I JUST FEEL SORRY
FOR THE GUY.

16:04.040 --> 16:06.250
MAKING TARGETS FEEL SPECIAL --
THAT'S HER THING.

16:06.250 --> 16:08.170
YOU KNOW, WHEN I GAVE HER
MY NAN'S PEARL EARRINGS,

16:08.170 --> 16:09.210
SHE WAS LIKE --

16:09.210 --> 16:10.540
YOU KNOW I DON'T LIKE YOU,
RIGHT?

16:12.830 --> 16:15.080
I CALL THEM
SPLINTER BOMBS.

16:15.080 --> 16:17.210
HAS A NICE RING TO IT,
DOESN'T IT?

16:17.210 --> 16:18.880
IS THERE ANY WAY FOR ME

16:18.880 --> 16:21.330
TO GET MY HANDS
ON A SPLINTER BOMB?

16:21.330 --> 16:23.210
THOSE REALLY ARE
A THING OF BEAUTY.

16:23.210 --> 16:27.620
UNFORTUNATELY, I SHIPPED
THEM ALL OUT YESTERDAY.

16:27.620 --> 16:30.620
PLUS, I CAN'T TAKE
ALL THE CREDIT.

16:30.620 --> 16:34.620
ORIGINAL SPECS CAME FROM
HYDRA TECHNOLOGY WAY BACK WHEN.

16:34.620 --> 16:36.000
WHITEHALL GAVE THEM
TO YOU?

16:36.000 --> 16:38.540
YES. A LEAP OF FAITH.

16:38.540 --> 16:41.040
I JUST HOPE I'VE EARNED A CHANCE
TO WORK ON THE DIVINER.

16:41.040 --> 16:42.460
THE DIVINER?

16:42.460 --> 16:45.170
THAT'S WHAT THE LUNATIC
WHO BROUGHT IT TO HIM
CALLS IT, ANYWAY.

16:47.790 --> 16:49.250
I HEARD IT'S ALIEN.

16:49.250 --> 16:50.790
YOU DON'T THINK
HE MEANS --

16:50.790 --> 16:52.080
THE OBELISK.

16:52.080 --> 16:53.040
[ TABLET BEEPING ]

16:53.040 --> 16:55.000
TOSHIRO'S PEOPLE HAVE
AN INCOMING MESSAGE.

16:57.210 --> 16:58.380
OH, NO.

16:58.380 --> 16:59.750
WHAT?

17:01.620 --> 17:04.000
ALL I KNOW IS THAT I HAVE
A BETTER CASE TO MAKE

17:04.000 --> 17:06.250
ONCE SCARLOTTI'S TEAM
GETS TO BECKERS.

17:06.250 --> 17:09.000
THEN S.H.I.E.L.D.
WILL BE DEAD IN THE WATER.

17:09.000 --> 17:10.880
THEY'RE EN ROUTE
TO BECKERS NOW?

17:13.460 --> 17:15.000
[ GUNSHOT ]

17:24.460 --> 17:26.579
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

17:26.579 --> 17:28.710
YOU CAN THANK ME LATER.

17:28.710 --> 17:30.080
THANK YOU?
WHAT THE HELL WERE YOU THINKING?

17:30.080 --> 17:31.460
WHAT WAS I THINKING?
I JUST SAVED YOUR LIFE.

17:31.460 --> 17:32.920
YOU DON'T THINK I KNEW
THAT GUY WAS BEHIND ME?

17:32.920 --> 17:34.620
THIS -- THIS IS JUST
YOU PEACOCKING.

17:34.620 --> 17:36.460
HE MADE YOU,
AND HE WAS GONNA KILL YOU!

17:36.460 --> 17:38.380
AND, SWEETHEART, NOBODY USES
THE WORD "PEACOCKING."

17:38.380 --> 17:39.620
[ SCOFFS ]

17:39.620 --> 17:40.960
ARE YOU EVEN LISTENING
TO YOURSELF RIGHT NOW?

17:40.960 --> 17:42.080
OH, WAIT.
OF COURSE YOU ARE.

17:42.080 --> 17:43.500
YOU LOVE THE SOUND
OF YOUR OWN VOICE.

17:43.500 --> 17:45.170
BECAUSE IT'S REASONABLE.
ONE OF US HAS TO BE.

17:45.170 --> 17:46.540
THIS IS WHAT MAKES YOU
SO AGGRAVATING TO BE WITH.

17:46.540 --> 17:48.330
HENCE, NOT WITH ME ANYMORE.
LUCKY US.
YES.

17:48.330 --> 17:50.000
REALLY?

17:50.000 --> 17:53.120
I JUST SAVED HER LIFE TWICE,
AND THIS IS THE THANKS I GET.

17:55.330 --> 17:57.080
TOSHIRO SAID THAT THEY WERE
GOING AFTER BECKERS.

17:57.080 --> 17:58.330
RECOGNIZE THE NAME?

17:58.330 --> 18:00.500
YEAH, JULIEN BECKERS, BELGIAN
FOREIGN AFFAIRS MINISTER.

18:00.500 --> 18:02.170
THE GUY WHO'S BEEN
KEEPING THE PEACE?

18:02.170 --> 18:04.080
IF SCARLOTTI'S TEAM
TAKES OUT BECKERS,

18:04.080 --> 18:05.460
EVEN THE NEUTRAL
U.N. COUNTRIES

18:05.460 --> 18:07.500
ARE GONNA FALL IN LINE
WITH SENATOR WARD'S PROPOSAL.

18:07.500 --> 18:10.080
CALL COULSON.
WE'RE HEADING TO BELGIUM.

18:10.080 --> 18:11.330
BAD DAY
TO BE S.H.I.E.L.D., EH?

18:15.000 --> 18:18.500
I STILL CAN'T FIND ANYTHING
ON THE WEAPONS.

18:18.500 --> 18:19.750
FITZ?

18:24.330 --> 18:27.670
AH, YOU'RE STILL LOOKING
AT THOSE BACKLOGGED FILES.

18:27.670 --> 18:29.500
YEAH.

18:29.500 --> 18:31.790
THAT'S BECAUSE, UM...

18:31.790 --> 18:36.210
THOSE -- THESE TWO BITS,
THERE'S SOMETHING.

18:36.210 --> 18:38.880
I THINK THE --
A SIMILAR ALLOY?

18:38.880 --> 18:40.000
NO, NO.

18:40.000 --> 18:41.290
NO. UM, NO.

18:41.290 --> 18:43.920
IT'S...UM...

18:43.920 --> 18:46.960
IT'S IMPORTANT,
BECAUSE...

18:46.960 --> 18:50.000
I...THE...

18:50.000 --> 18:51.750
[ GROANS ] CAN YOU STOP,

18:51.750 --> 18:52.790
UH...STOP LOOKING AT ME?

18:52.790 --> 18:54.040
OH, I CAN'T EVEN
LOOK AT YOU NOW.

18:54.040 --> 18:55.210
NO, NOT LIKE THAT,
YOU CAN'T.

18:55.210 --> 18:56.880
LIKE WHAT? I'M --

18:56.880 --> 18:59.290
I'M TRYING NOT TO TREAT YOU
ANY DIFFERENTLY THAN --

18:59.290 --> 19:01.000
I KNOW,
BUT I AM DIFFERENT.

19:01.000 --> 19:02.080
AND I -- AND I'M --

19:02.080 --> 19:04.420
I'M TRYING NOT TO BE,
BUT I AM.

19:06.540 --> 19:08.830
AND IF FOR SOME REASON
YOU CAN'T ACCEPT IT --

19:08.830 --> 19:10.790
OH, THAT'S NOT FAIR.

19:10.790 --> 19:12.830
FITZ, I'M ONLY TRYING
TO HELP.

19:12.830 --> 19:14.380
YOU LEFT.

19:14.380 --> 19:16.120
I NEEDED HELP.

19:16.120 --> 19:17.960
I NEEDED HELP
WITH THE CLOAKING.

19:17.960 --> 19:21.330
I NEEDED HELP WITH, UM --
WITH LOTS OF OTHER THINGS,

19:21.330 --> 19:24.880
AND SOMEONE TO TALK THROUGH,
AT LEAST.

19:24.880 --> 19:27.000
YOU GAVE UP ON ME.

19:27.000 --> 19:28.420
I DID NO SUCH THING.

19:28.420 --> 19:29.540
YOU TOLD ME
YOU WERE GONNA GO SEE

19:29.540 --> 19:30.540
YOUR MUM AND YOUR DAD,

19:30.540 --> 19:32.250
AND THEN YOU WENT OFF TO --
FOR ALL I --

19:32.250 --> 19:33.830
FOR ALL I KNOW, YOU COULD --
SOMETHING COULD'VE --

19:33.830 --> 19:34.880
YOU COULD'VE BEEN KILLED.

19:34.880 --> 19:36.750
AND BECAUSE WHAT?

19:36.750 --> 19:38.670
BECAUSE YOU THINK
I'M USELESS?

19:38.670 --> 19:41.120
OF COURSE I DON'T.
THAT'S NOT WHY I LEFT.

19:41.120 --> 19:42.670
WELL, THEN, WHY?

19:42.670 --> 19:43.750
[ SIGHS ]

19:45.790 --> 19:46.790
FITZ...

19:49.830 --> 19:51.790
I'M SORRY.
I CAN'T DO THIS.

19:51.790 --> 19:53.420
EXCUSE ME.

20:10.500 --> 20:12.380
EXCUSE ME.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

20:12.380 --> 20:13.920
DON'T WORRY.

20:13.920 --> 20:15.830
I HAVEN'T BEEN WAITING LONG.

20:15.830 --> 20:18.040
PHIL COULSON.

20:22.460 --> 20:24.290
I ASSUME THESE
ARE FOR YOUR SPEECH.

20:24.290 --> 20:26.460
I MADE A FEW CHANGES.

20:26.460 --> 20:27.750
IT'S FUNNIER NOW.

20:30.000 --> 20:32.210
I'M SURE TALBOT'S MENTIONED ME
FROM TIME TO TIME,

20:32.210 --> 20:34.960
WHICH IS PERHAPS WHY
YOU'RE TRYING TO CALL...

20:34.960 --> 20:37.380
[ STATIC ]
...WHOMEVER IT IS
YOU'RE TRYING TO CALL.

20:37.380 --> 20:40.460
ALSO, YOUR MEN
WON'T BE CHECKING ON YOU --

20:40.460 --> 20:42.210
AT LEAST NOT FOR
THE NEXT HOUR.

20:42.210 --> 20:43.750
YOU'VE REQUESTED
SOME "ME" TIME.

20:43.750 --> 20:46.170
AND WHO CAN ARGUE
WITH THAT?

20:46.170 --> 20:47.670
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

20:47.670 --> 20:49.250
AN OPPORTUNITY
TO CLEAR THE AIR.

20:49.250 --> 20:50.960
THE ATTACK ON THE U.N.

20:50.960 --> 20:52.670
WASN'T S.H.I.E.L.D.,
IT WAS HYDRA --

20:52.670 --> 20:54.420
SPECIFICALLY,
A MAN NAMED DANIEL WHITEHALL.

20:54.420 --> 20:56.750
YOU DIDN'T COME HERE
TO CLEAR THE AIR.

20:56.750 --> 20:58.830
YOU NEED SOMETHING
FROM ME.

20:58.830 --> 21:00.960
AND ALL THIS SWAGGERING
SIMPLY TELLS ME

21:00.960 --> 21:02.830
YOU HAVE NOTHING TO OFFER
IN RETURN.

21:02.830 --> 21:05.380
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME
TO DO?

21:05.380 --> 21:09.540
GO ON RECORD DEFENDING
S.H.I.E.L.D., CONDEMNING HYDRA?

21:09.540 --> 21:10.960
THE AMERICAN PEOPLE

21:10.960 --> 21:12.830
ARE LOOKING FOR A SIMPLE ENEMY,
MR. COULSON.

21:12.830 --> 21:15.960
IT'S WHAT MAKES THEM
FEEL SAFE.

21:15.960 --> 21:17.330
AND HOW DO THEY THINK
THEY'D FEEL

21:17.330 --> 21:18.830
IF THEY KNEW
YOUR BROTHER WAS HYDRA?

21:20.830 --> 21:23.330
THAT'S AN AWFULLY
COMPLICATED IDEA TO GRASP,

21:23.330 --> 21:24.790
ESPECIALLY
IN AN ELECTION YEAR.

21:26.880 --> 21:29.170
ARE YOU THREATENING ME,
MR. COULSON?

21:29.170 --> 21:30.710
NO.

21:30.710 --> 21:32.920
I'M TELLING YOU I HAVE
YOUR BROTHER IN MY BASEMENT.

21:37.960 --> 21:39.670
[ DOOR BEEPS ]

21:42.540 --> 21:44.500
YOU'RE BACK.

21:48.380 --> 21:49.920
CAMERA'S OFF.

21:49.920 --> 21:51.620
DOES COULSON KNOW THAT --

21:51.620 --> 21:53.330
COULSON'S OUT.

21:53.330 --> 21:57.120
HE CUT US OFF LAST TIME,
BUT NOW NOBODY'S WATCHING.

21:57.120 --> 22:00.830
JUST YOU AND ME.

22:00.830 --> 22:04.710
IS HE ALL RIGHT?
IS GRANT HURT?

22:04.710 --> 22:06.670
DID -- DID YOU
HAVE TO DO ANYTHING --

22:06.670 --> 22:08.080
NO.

22:08.080 --> 22:09.210
WE BELIEVE
THERE ARE OTHER WAYS

22:09.210 --> 22:10.330
TO GET INFORMATION
FROM PEOPLE.

22:10.330 --> 22:12.250
[ SIGHS ]

22:12.250 --> 22:14.420
I'M SURPRISED
YOUR CONCERNED, HONESTLY.

22:14.420 --> 22:17.040
YOU DON'T HAVE A BROTHER,
DO YOU?

22:17.040 --> 22:18.460
NO.

22:18.460 --> 22:20.420
ALWAYS WANTED ONE,
THOUGH.

22:20.420 --> 22:26.880
AS AN ONLY CHILD, YOU TEND
TO IDEALIZE THAT RELATIONSHIP.

22:26.880 --> 22:29.670
FAMILY HAS TO TAKE CARE OF
EACH OTHER, RIGHT?

22:29.670 --> 22:32.330
THEN AGAIN...

22:32.330 --> 22:34.000
I'VE HEARD SOME STORIES
THAT SAY OTHERWISE.

22:34.000 --> 22:35.880
WHAT DID GRANT TELL YOU?

22:35.880 --> 22:38.330
PLENTY.

22:38.330 --> 22:39.420
I KNOW WHAT YOU DID.

22:41.500 --> 22:43.670
HOW YOU FORCED HIM TO TORTURE
YOUR YOUNGEST BROTHER.

22:43.670 --> 22:45.000
I KNOW WHAT HAPPENED
AT THE WELL.

22:47.080 --> 22:49.290
SO, IT'S A WELL NOW?

22:54.250 --> 22:57.000
YOU MAY THINK YOU KNOW
GRANT WARD, MR. COULSON,

22:57.000 --> 23:00.330
BUT TRUST ME --
UNDERNEATH EVERY LIE HE TELLS

23:00.330 --> 23:01.710
IS JUST ANOTHER LIE.

23:01.710 --> 23:03.960
Ward: IS COULSON
TALKING TO CHRISTIAN?

23:05.620 --> 23:07.580
YOU CAN'T TRUST HIM.

23:07.580 --> 23:09.880
HE'LL SMILE, BARE HIS SOUL.

23:09.880 --> 23:11.580
IT IS ALL MANIPULATION.

23:11.580 --> 23:13.250
HE IS A MASTER AT IT.

23:13.250 --> 23:17.040
[ SIGHS ]
LOOK, I KNOW WHAT I AM.

23:17.040 --> 23:19.420
BUT MY BROTHER...

23:19.420 --> 23:21.790
[ SIGHS ]

23:21.790 --> 23:23.580
HE'S WORSE.

23:23.580 --> 23:27.540
WHEN WE WERE KIDS,
OUR PARENTS WERE ALWAYS GONE --

23:27.540 --> 23:29.790
SOME STATE FUNCTION
OR ANOTHER.

23:29.790 --> 23:32.330
WE'D SPEND ALL DAY
BY THE CREEK

23:32.330 --> 23:34.290
HUNTING SALAMANDERS
AND CRAYFISH.

23:34.290 --> 23:39.250
BUT I COULD NEVER
LEAVE GRANT ALONE WITH THOMAS.

23:39.250 --> 23:42.250
I FOUND GRANT
DOWN THERE ONCE,

23:42.250 --> 23:44.710
STANDING OVER HIM
WITH A SCREWDRIVER.

23:44.710 --> 23:50.000
THOMAS WAS ON THE GROUND,
JUST SCREAMING.

23:50.000 --> 23:51.580
AND I SAW SOMETHING...

23:54.170 --> 23:56.710
SOMETHING ELSE
BEHIND HIS EYES.

23:56.710 --> 24:00.920
SOMETHING I'M SURE
YOU'VE SEEN BEFORE, AS WELL.

24:00.920 --> 24:02.460
[ SIGHS ]

24:02.460 --> 24:03.880
A SECOND LATER,
IT WAS GONE,

24:03.880 --> 24:06.210
AND HE WAS JUST
MY LITTLE BROTHER AGAIN.

24:08.500 --> 24:12.170
HE TOLD OUR PARENTS
I FORCED HIM TO DO IT.

24:12.170 --> 24:18.670
I'VE SPENT TOO MUCH OF MY LIFE
TRYING TO UNRAVEL HIS LIES.

24:19.710 --> 24:21.330
SO HAVE I.

24:21.330 --> 24:26.750
AND YET,
HE KEEPS TELLING THEM.

24:26.750 --> 24:29.580
HE ALWAYS FINDS SOMEONE
TO BELIEVE HIM.

24:29.580 --> 24:31.710
Ward:
I'M TELLING YOU THE TRUTH.

24:31.710 --> 24:34.500
YOU SEE THAT NOW,
DON'T YOU?

24:34.500 --> 24:36.920
I NEVER LIED
ABOUT YOUR FATHER.

24:36.920 --> 24:39.460
YOU JUST DIDN'T GIVE ME
THE CHANCE TO TELL YOU --

24:39.460 --> 24:41.670
I KNOW.

24:41.670 --> 24:43.250
BUT I'M GIVING YOU
THE CHANCE NOW.

24:45.670 --> 24:47.210
AND I WANT TO KNOW
EVERYTHING.

24:47.210 --> 24:49.500
HE WON'T GET AWAY WITH IT
THIS TIME.

24:53.620 --> 24:55.580
IT'S NOT GOING
TO BE SIMPLE...

24:57.460 --> 24:59.830
...BUT I THINK I KNOW A WAY
WE CAN BOTH HAVE WHAT WE WANT.

25:02.960 --> 25:06.170
YOUR FATHER
KILLED PEOPLE, YES.

25:06.170 --> 25:09.170
BUT EVERYTHING
HE DID, SKYE,

25:09.170 --> 25:11.000
HE DID BECAUSE
HE LOVED YOU.

25:12.880 --> 25:14.210
I CAN'T FAULT HIM
FOR THAT.

25:15.540 --> 25:18.080
THE PEOPLE WHO DIED
IN THE HUNAN PROVINCE,

25:18.080 --> 25:20.710
THEY WEREN'T VILLAGERS.

25:20.710 --> 25:21.880
THEY WERE HYDRA AGENTS.

25:23.500 --> 25:24.830
THEY'D FOUND YOU
AND YOUR MOTHER.

25:24.830 --> 25:26.710
MY MOTHER?

25:28.420 --> 25:29.880
IS SHE ALIVE, TOO?

25:29.880 --> 25:31.710
NO.

25:31.710 --> 25:33.580
NO, THEY KILLED HER.

25:35.250 --> 25:36.290
WHY?

25:36.290 --> 25:37.580
I DON'T KNOW.

25:40.250 --> 25:43.620
BUT WHEN YOUR FATHER GOT THERE,
HE LOST IT,

25:43.620 --> 25:46.460
TORE UP THE WHOLE VILLAGE
AND EVERYONE IN IT.

25:46.460 --> 25:48.540
HOW?

25:48.540 --> 25:50.380
WHAT IS HE?

25:50.380 --> 25:52.500
WHATEVER HE IS,

25:52.500 --> 25:56.460
HE LOST HIS WHOLE FAMILY
IN ONE DAY, AND HE CRACKED.

25:56.460 --> 25:58.790
BUT NOW HE WANTS TO
PUT THAT FAMILY BACK TOGETHER.

25:58.790 --> 26:00.620
I CAN HELP WITH THAT.

26:00.620 --> 26:02.380
I CAN TAKE YOU TO HIM.

26:02.380 --> 26:04.460
HOW?

26:04.460 --> 26:05.580
WHERE IS HE?

26:05.580 --> 26:07.250
I'VE GOT CONNECTIONS.

26:08.500 --> 26:09.710
PEOPLE I CAN TALK TO
WILL TRACK HIM --

26:09.710 --> 26:10.960
WHAT CONNECTIONS?

26:10.960 --> 26:12.210
WHAT PEOPLE?

26:12.210 --> 26:13.460
RAINA'S GONE.

26:13.460 --> 26:15.540
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M RESOURCEFUL.

26:15.540 --> 26:16.580
THEN TELL ME
WHAT YOU KNOW.

26:18.000 --> 26:19.670
ISN'T THERE
ANYTHING ELSE?

26:21.580 --> 26:23.620
PLEASE, WARD.

26:23.620 --> 26:25.420
NO.

26:25.420 --> 26:28.830
BUT WE CAN FIND HIM
TOGETHER.

26:31.540 --> 26:33.080
I PROMISE YOU.

26:35.170 --> 26:38.080
THANK YOU FOR TELLING ME
EVERYTHING YOU KNOW.

26:39.620 --> 26:41.040
IT'S TIME
WE GET YOU OUT OF HERE.

26:42.540 --> 26:43.540
REALLY?

26:43.540 --> 26:45.460
REALLY.

26:47.000 --> 26:48.500
YOU'RE BEING TRANSFERRED,
WARD.

26:48.500 --> 26:51.080
YOUR BROTHER WANTS YOU
IN HIS CUSTODY,

26:51.080 --> 26:54.080
AND WE'RE GONNA GIVE HIM
EXACTLY WHAT HE WANTS.

26:59.880 --> 27:01.330
I STRUCK A DEAL
WITH THE SENATOR.

27:01.330 --> 27:03.000
HE'LL REVERSE
HIS ANTI-S.H.I.E.L.D. PROPOSAL

27:03.000 --> 27:04.250
IN EXCHANGE
FOR HIS BROTHER.

27:04.250 --> 27:05.500
LONG TIME COMING.

27:05.500 --> 27:07.380
And Skye?
I GOT EVERYTHING
I NEEDED.

27:07.380 --> 27:08.540
Good.

27:08.540 --> 27:10.330
WE'LL TOUCH DOWN
IN BELGIUM SOON --

27:10.330 --> 27:12.790
TRY TO GET TO BECKERS
BEFORE WHITEHALL'S TEAM DOES.

27:12.790 --> 27:14.750
I DON'T HAVE TO REMIND YOU
THAT IF HE'S KILLED,

27:14.750 --> 27:16.080
THE U.N. WILL
COME AFTER US

27:16.080 --> 27:17.750
NO MATTER WHAT THE SENATOR SAYS
OR DOES.

27:17.750 --> 27:20.120
WE'LL BE IN TOUCH.

27:20.120 --> 27:22.540
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

27:26.420 --> 27:28.120
WE GOT BECKERS' LOCATION.

27:32.500 --> 27:34.080
Fitz:
YES, THEORETICALLY,

27:34.080 --> 27:36.420
ALL THOSE POINTS
HAVE TO BE CONNECTED.

27:36.420 --> 27:38.250
Mack:
[ CHUCKLES ] DAMN, FITZ.

27:38.250 --> 27:40.500
YOU'RE RIGHT.
YOU'RE RIGHT.

27:40.500 --> 27:41.500
AH.

27:41.500 --> 27:42.750
WHY DO YOU LOOK
SO SURPRISED?

27:42.750 --> 27:43.790
WELL...

27:43.790 --> 27:45.120
WELL, YEAH.

27:45.120 --> 27:46.420
WELL, I'D PROBABLY BE
SURPRISED -- HEY, SIMMONS.

27:48.210 --> 27:49.330
THE EXPLOSIVES --
MACK WAS JUST --

27:49.330 --> 27:50.460
HE SAW THE, UM...

27:50.460 --> 27:52.880
YEAH, HE KEPT MENTIONING
BACKLOGGED FILES,

27:52.880 --> 27:54.790
AND, YOU KNOW, HALF THE STUFF
HE SAYS IS NONSENSE.

27:54.790 --> 27:56.330
NO, IT'S NOT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

27:56.330 --> 27:58.330
CHECK THIS OUT.

27:58.330 --> 28:00.500
IT TURNS OUT THESE BOMBS
ARE ACTUALLY FROM THE 1940s,

28:00.500 --> 28:02.420
AND THEY WERE DEVELOPED
BY A HYDRA SCIENTIST

28:02.420 --> 28:03.420
THAT WORKED FOR

28:03.420 --> 28:04.880
THE RED SKULL.
THE RED SKULL.

28:04.880 --> 28:06.250
NOT NONSENSE,
AND DESIGNER.

28:06.250 --> 28:08.080
YEAH, AND THE ACTUAL DESIGNER
OF THE BOMBS

28:08.080 --> 28:09.670
IS A GUY NAMED...

28:09.670 --> 28:11.040
VINCENT BECKERS.
VINCENT BECKERS.

28:11.040 --> 28:12.170
VINCENT BECKERS.

28:13.330 --> 28:17.500
WE NEED TO FIND COULSON --
NOW.

28:17.500 --> 28:19.290
Ward:
LISTEN TO ME.

28:19.290 --> 28:21.750
YOU CAN'T TRUST HIM.

28:21.750 --> 28:23.170
THREE AND A HALF WEEKS.

28:24.330 --> 28:27.540
I SAT IN THIS CHAIR EVERY DAY
FOR THREE AND A HALF WEEKS,

28:27.540 --> 28:29.170
AND YOU NEVER SAID A WORD.

28:29.170 --> 28:30.960
BUT NOW YOU WANT TO TALK?

28:32.000 --> 28:33.330
WELL, IT'S TOO LATE.

28:33.330 --> 28:34.750
EVERYTHING I TOLD SKYE
WAS TRUE.

28:34.750 --> 28:36.000
YOU KNOW THAT.

28:36.000 --> 28:38.500
I HAVEN'T GIVEN YOU
ONE BAD PIECE OF INTEL.

28:38.500 --> 28:39.620
IS THAT WORTH NOTHING?

28:39.620 --> 28:42.330
YOU WILL NEVER
SEE SKYE AGAIN.

28:43.420 --> 28:46.170
I THOUGHT WE WERE REBUILDING
TRUST, COULSON.

28:47.290 --> 28:49.830
I CAN HELP YOU.

28:49.830 --> 28:51.420
I'M STILL
A PART OF YOUR TEAM.

28:51.420 --> 28:53.120
MY TEAM?

28:53.120 --> 28:54.670
YOU TH--

28:57.000 --> 29:00.460
YOU ARE NOT
NOR WILL YOU EVER BE ON MY TEAM.

29:01.580 --> 29:04.380
YOU DROPPED FITZ-SIMMONS
OUT OF A PLANE.

29:04.380 --> 29:07.210
YOU MURDERED VICTORIA HAND
AND ERIC KOENIG.

29:07.210 --> 29:10.000
YOU BETRAYED EVERY ONE OF US,
YOU DELUDED SON OF A BITCH.

29:10.000 --> 29:14.120
THE ONLY REASON YOU'RE ALIVE
IS BECAUSE YOU WERE OF USE.

29:14.120 --> 29:16.420
AND THE ONLY REASON
YOU'RE BEING TRANSFERRED

29:16.420 --> 29:18.420
IS BECAUSE YOUR BROTHER
IS OF MORE USE.

29:20.290 --> 29:25.000
WAS THIS HIS IDEA OR YOURS
TO PUT ME ON TRIAL?

29:25.000 --> 29:26.790
HMM?

29:26.790 --> 29:28.290
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

29:29.420 --> 29:31.920
IT'S A GOOD STORY --

29:31.920 --> 29:34.750
A MAN BRAVE ENOUGH
TO HAVE HIS OWN BROTHER EXECUTED

29:34.750 --> 29:36.000
FOR HIS CRIMES.

29:36.000 --> 29:38.420
OH, CHRISTIAN WILL MILK THAT
FOR ALL IT'S WORTH.

29:40.120 --> 29:42.580
AND THE TRIAL SHOULD WRAP UP
RIGHT BEFORE THE MIDTERMS.

29:42.580 --> 29:44.880
YOUR BROTHER SAW
THE SAME ANGLES.

29:46.330 --> 29:48.620
MAYBE YOU TWO ARE MORE ALIKE
THAN YOU THINK.

29:48.620 --> 29:50.420
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING ]

29:52.040 --> 29:53.620
SIR, WE NEED YOU.

29:59.040 --> 30:01.580
Simmons: VINCENT BECKERS
IS JULIEN'S GRANDFATHER.

30:01.580 --> 30:04.120
WE BELIEVE THE HYDRA CONNECTION
STAYED VERY MUCH ALIVE.

30:04.120 --> 30:06.380
WE FOUND THE TRAVEL RECORDS FOR
BECKERS AND WHITEHALL, AND...

30:06.380 --> 30:09.710
THEY COINCIDED AT LEAST 12 TIMES
OVER THE PAST FIVE YEARS.

30:09.710 --> 30:10.710
THAT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

30:10.710 --> 30:12.210
YEAH, WHY WOULD HYDRA
BE TARGETING

30:12.210 --> 30:13.250
ONE OF THEIR OWN
OPERATIVES?

30:14.500 --> 30:16.790
WE'VE BEEN PLAYED.
GET MAY ON THE LINE.

30:16.790 --> 30:19.290
THEY NEED TO REROUTE
TO OUR SAFE HOUSE IN BRUGES.

30:19.290 --> 30:21.170
[ DOOR BEEPS ]

30:36.250 --> 30:38.330
Walters:
MR. BECKERS.

30:38.330 --> 30:40.380
WE HAVE AGENTS
LOOKING FOR YOU.

30:40.380 --> 30:42.460
HOW DID YOU FIND
THIS PLACE?

30:42.460 --> 30:44.120
I FOLLOWED THEM HERE.

30:47.920 --> 30:51.210
[ BEEPING ]

30:51.210 --> 30:53.290
SIR,
MAY'S TEAM'S EN ROUTE.

30:55.330 --> 30:56.460
OH, NO.

30:58.290 --> 31:01.500
WHITEHALL DIDN'T JUST WANT TO
TURN THE WORLD AGAINST US.

31:01.500 --> 31:04.920
HE USED BECKERS AS A PROP
TO MAKE OUR OPERATIVES BELIEVE

31:04.920 --> 31:08.380
HIS COUNTRY WOULD PROVIDE
SAFE HAVEN, BUT IT'S A TRAP.

31:08.380 --> 31:09.460
THEY'LL BE FISH
IN A BARREL.

31:09.460 --> 31:11.330
WHAT THE HELL
DID YOU DO?

31:11.330 --> 31:12.920
[ GRUNTING ]

31:19.380 --> 31:20.790
[ GRUNTS ]

31:20.790 --> 31:22.120
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

31:24.620 --> 31:29.750
MR. SCARLOTTI, I'LL LEAVE YOU
TO WHAT YOU DO BEST.

31:39.920 --> 31:41.790
[ GRUNTS ]

31:45.080 --> 31:47.000
SHAME.

31:47.000 --> 31:49.210
I PREFER
TO TAKE MY TIME.

31:50.500 --> 31:53.250
[ SPLINTER BOMB WHIRRING ]

31:57.790 --> 31:59.670
HYDRA WILL NEVER DEFEAT --

32:00.790 --> 32:02.290
YOU WERE SAYING?

32:06.420 --> 32:07.580
[ GUNS COCK ]

32:07.580 --> 32:09.080
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

32:09.080 --> 32:11.380
HAIL HYDRA, GUYS.
HAIL HYDRA.

32:12.670 --> 32:13.670
I'M UNARMED.

32:13.670 --> 32:15.580
I'M NOT LOOKING
FOR ANY TROUBLE.

32:15.580 --> 32:16.880
WHO SENT YOU?

32:16.880 --> 32:18.210
HAVE YOU TRIED THE BEER
AROUND HERE?

32:18.210 --> 32:20.290
THIS IS
FROM STRAFFE HENDRIK,

32:20.290 --> 32:21.380
LITTLE BREWERY
AROUND THE CORNER.

32:21.380 --> 32:22.580
ASK FOR ZOE.

32:22.580 --> 32:24.880
SHE'LL HOOK YOU UP.

32:24.880 --> 32:26.380
HERE, SWEETHEART,
YOU CAN HAVE THE FIRST ONE.

32:26.380 --> 32:28.420
LOOKS LIKE
YOU COULD USE IT.

32:28.420 --> 32:29.920
THAT FACE -- SO DOUR.

32:29.920 --> 32:31.120
YOU GOT 10 SECONDS

32:31.120 --> 32:32.250
TO TELL ME EXACTLY
WHAT YOU'RE DOING HERE.

32:32.250 --> 32:35.250
I'M A MERC, MATE,
LIKE YOU LOT.

32:35.250 --> 32:36.120
AND IF YOU'RE LOOKING

32:36.120 --> 32:37.540
TO TAKE OUT
A FEW S.H.I.E.L.D. AGENTS

32:37.540 --> 32:39.500
HIGHER UP THE FOOD CHAIN,

32:39.500 --> 32:41.670
I HAPPEN
TO KNOW A COUPLE.

32:42.790 --> 32:46.620
THEY JUST NEED ABOUT 90 SECONDS
TO GET IN POSITION.

32:46.620 --> 32:48.080
HUH?

32:54.580 --> 32:56.250
[ GRUNTING ]

32:56.250 --> 32:57.540
LOOK OUT!

33:17.830 --> 33:19.080
ALL ALONE?

33:29.670 --> 33:31.170
BOBBI!

33:57.170 --> 33:58.580
BOB!

33:58.580 --> 34:00.250
[ WHIRRING ]

34:00.250 --> 34:02.080
[ GROANS ]

34:02.080 --> 34:03.080
THIRD TIME TODAY.

34:07.380 --> 34:09.120
WHAT?

34:09.120 --> 34:10.120
YOU SAVED MY LIFE.

34:13.000 --> 34:14.540
[ GRUNTING ]

34:23.830 --> 34:25.960
[ GROANING ]

34:33.380 --> 34:35.170
[ YELLS ]

34:36.380 --> 34:38.830
[ BEEPING ]

34:38.830 --> 34:40.580
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

34:40.580 --> 34:43.670
MAY...HOW MANY?

34:44.750 --> 34:45.790
[ SIGHS ]

34:47.460 --> 34:49.040
OKAY.

34:49.040 --> 34:51.710
GET HOME SAFE.

35:05.120 --> 35:07.040
Simmons: IT'S FUNNY.

35:07.040 --> 35:08.420
THIS IS WHERE
WE USED TO KEEP

35:08.420 --> 35:10.210
THE HAZARDOUS
BIOLOGICAL MATERIALS.

35:10.210 --> 35:11.420
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:11.420 --> 35:14.330
GUESS NOT EVERYTHING CHANGES,
HUH?

35:14.330 --> 35:16.080
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

35:16.080 --> 35:19.580
I JUST WANTED TO
THANK YOU

35:19.580 --> 35:20.920
FOR HELPING FITZ.

35:20.920 --> 35:24.000
WELL, FOR --
FOR BEING HIS FRIEND.

35:24.000 --> 35:26.460
I DON'T HELP HIM.

35:26.460 --> 35:28.000
HE DOESN'T NEED ANY.

35:28.000 --> 35:29.880
YOU KNOW, THAT GUY
YOU'RE WISHING HE WOULD BE --

35:29.880 --> 35:31.000
I NEVER MET HIM.

35:31.000 --> 35:33.170
I ONLY KNOW THIS GUY,
AND, UH...

35:33.170 --> 35:35.460
YEAH, I MEAN,
HE'S A LITTLE WEIRD,

35:35.460 --> 35:38.960
BUT, UH --
BUT I LIKE HIM.

35:38.960 --> 35:42.670
I DON'T WANT HIM TO BE
ANYBODY BUT HIMSELF.

35:42.670 --> 35:43.790
YOU SURE ABOUT THAT?

35:43.790 --> 35:45.000
YES.

35:45.000 --> 35:46.920
BECAUSE I HEARD
HE TOLD YOU HOW HE FELT

35:46.920 --> 35:48.170
AND YOU BAILED.

35:49.880 --> 35:51.380
THAT'S NOT WHAT HAPPENED.

35:51.380 --> 35:52.920
LOOK...

35:54.170 --> 35:56.670
...I KNOW
YOU TWO HAVE A PAST.

35:56.670 --> 35:58.040
BUT FROM WHAT I'VE SEEN,

35:58.040 --> 36:00.880
THE ONLY THING
THAT MAKES HIM WORSE...

36:02.170 --> 36:03.540
...IS YOU.

36:04.880 --> 36:07.960
I KNOW.

36:07.960 --> 36:10.620
WHY DO YOU THINK I LEFT?

36:14.210 --> 36:16.040
Bobbi:
YOU'RE LEAVING.

36:24.420 --> 36:25.880
S.H.I.E.L.D.'s ALWAYS BEEN
YOUR THING.

36:25.880 --> 36:27.960
I WON'T STAND IN THE WAY
OF THAT.

36:29.620 --> 36:31.420
S.H.I.E.L.D.'s
NOT S.H.I.E.L.D. ANYMORE.

36:32.710 --> 36:35.710
I'M STILL TRYING TO FIGURE OUT
WHERE I FIT IN, TOO.

36:42.620 --> 36:44.830
JUST DON'T DIE OUT THERE,
ALL RIGHT?

36:48.880 --> 36:51.960
BUT IF YOU WANT TO STAY...

36:51.960 --> 36:54.120
STAY.

37:01.500 --> 37:02.880
TIME TO GO.

37:05.790 --> 37:07.670
[ DEVICE BEEPS ]

37:12.920 --> 37:14.620
HANDS.

37:16.500 --> 37:19.380
[ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]

37:22.500 --> 37:24.620
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

37:24.620 --> 37:29.580
DIGNITARIES,
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

37:29.580 --> 37:31.290
LESS THAN 48 HOURS AGO,

37:31.290 --> 37:33.420
BRAVE MEN AND WOMEN
LOST THEIR LIVES

37:33.420 --> 37:35.500
AT THIS VERY SPOT
I'M STANDING NOW,

37:35.500 --> 37:39.580
AND I THINK WE OWE IT TO THEM
TO DISCUSS SOMETHING

37:39.580 --> 37:43.330
ALL TOO OFTEN ELUSIVE --
THE TRUTH.

37:45.210 --> 37:48.790
SOMETIMES WE WANT THINGS SIMPLER
THAN THEY ACTUALLY ARE, BUT...

37:51.420 --> 37:54.790
...THE TOUGH REALITY IS,
WE ARE COMPLEX CREATURES.

37:56.380 --> 37:58.580
SKYE.

37:58.580 --> 38:01.790
IF I EVER
SEE YOU AGAIN...

38:01.790 --> 38:02.960
I'LL KILL YOU.

38:02.960 --> 38:04.580
AND I'VE COME TO UNDERSTAND

38:04.580 --> 38:06.670
SOMETHING THAT WORLD MUST,
AS WELL.

38:06.670 --> 38:10.290
THERE IS A DIFFERENCE BETWEEN
S.H.I.E.L.D. AND HYDRA.

38:10.290 --> 38:12.960
ONE WAS AN ORGANIZATION
BUILT ON PROTECTION,

38:12.960 --> 38:15.210
AND THE OTHER --
WORLD DOMINATION.

38:15.210 --> 38:17.170
WE GOT BECKERS
AT THE BORDER.

38:23.880 --> 38:26.790
HOW MANY MEN
DID YOU LOSE?

38:26.790 --> 38:28.620
SIX.

38:30.380 --> 38:33.290
IT'S ALWAYS A SHAME
WHEN A GOOD SOLDIER FALLS.

38:40.670 --> 38:43.880
AND JUST AS GOOD AND EVIL
EXISTED SIDE-BY-SIDE

38:43.880 --> 38:45.540
WITHIN S.H.I.E.L.D.,

38:45.540 --> 38:48.040
THE SAME WAS TRUE
IN MY OWN HOME.

38:48.040 --> 38:52.250
AT FIRST, I WAS ASHAMED TO SHARE
THIS TRUTH WITH THE WORLD,

38:52.250 --> 38:55.120
BUT MY YOUNGER BROTHER,
GRANT WARD,

38:55.120 --> 38:56.880
WAS A MEMBER OF HYDRA.

38:56.880 --> 38:58.500
HE WAS A TRAITOR.

38:58.500 --> 39:03.920
HE WAS A TRAITOR TO HIS FRIENDS,
HIS FAMILY, AND HIS NATION.

39:07.250 --> 39:10.460
DO NOT GIVE HIM
ONE INCH.

39:16.420 --> 39:18.620
TELL SKYE
THIS DOESN'T CHANGE ANYTHING.

39:20.040 --> 39:21.960
I'LL KEEP MY PROMISE.

39:25.540 --> 39:28.790
WHEN EVIL SITS CLOSEST
TO ONE'S OWN HEART,

39:28.790 --> 39:31.790
THAT IS WHEN THE SUREST HAND
MUST CUT IT OUT.

39:31.790 --> 39:33.210
I GIVE MY WORD.

39:33.210 --> 39:35.790
I WILL PERSONALLY MAKE SURE

39:35.790 --> 39:38.710
MY BROTHER IS PUNISHED
FOR HIS CRIMES.

39:38.710 --> 39:42.830
BUT AS IS SO OFTEN TRUE,

39:42.830 --> 39:46.040
THE DARKNESS LINGERS LONGER
THAN THE LIGHT.

39:46.040 --> 39:50.500
AND WHILE S.H.I.E.L.D. IS GONE,
HYDRA IS A PROBLEM

39:50.500 --> 39:53.040
THAT THE WORLD MUST STILL FACE.
[ EXHALES SLOWLY ]

39:53.040 --> 39:56.290
Steward: OTHERWISE,
THAT DARKNESS WILL GROW

39:56.290 --> 39:57.290
AND SPREAD...

39:57.290 --> 39:58.290
[ BONE SNAPS ]

39:58.290 --> 40:00.880
...AND CAST A SHADOW
OVER US ALL.

40:03.620 --> 40:05.580
[ GRUNTING ]

40:08.120 --> 40:09.580
WE'LL RETURN IN A MOMENT.

40:13.710 --> 40:16.380
[ ROCK MUSIC PLAYING ]

40:19.040 --> 40:21.170
YOU GOT CASH THIS TIME?

40:27.580 --> 40:29.670
TONIGHT,
WE FINISH IT.

40:34.210 --> 40:36.710
IT'S GONNA HURT.

40:39.670 --> 40:41.290
THE REST PROBABLY
HASN'T HEALED YET.

40:41.290 --> 40:42.540
YOU SURE YOU DON'T WANT TO WAIT
A FEW DAYS?

40:42.540 --> 40:44.500
THE PAIN HELPS ME
REMEMBER.

40:53.380 --> 40:55.710
[ NEEDLE BUZZING ]
